Class EntityQuestStatusTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • world.story.EntityQuestStatusTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatabaseManager.DatabaseTable

    public class EntityQuestStatusTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements DatabaseManager.DatabaseTable
    Contains the table schema for a table relating players and quests. Used to store what quests are active for a player and what the status of each quest is for that player
